Class ArchiveService

java.lang.Object
com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.services.ArchiveService
@Service public class ArchiveService extends Object

This class is the Spring Boot service responsible for top-level actions used by the archive server controller.

  • Constructor Details

    • ArchiveService

      public ArchiveService(ArchiveIngestor archiveIngestor, ArchiveLogService logService, ArchiveMessageService messageService, ArchiveSessionService sessionService, ArchiveWebsocketService websocketService) throws InterruptedException

      This constructor injects services and values into the archive service.

      Parameters:
      archiveIngestor - The injected archive ingestor
      logService - The injected logging service.
      messageService - The injected message service.
      sessionService - The injected session service.
      websocketService - The injected websocket service.
      Throws:
      InterruptedException - If the Thread.sleep() line in sessionService.sessionTaskMonitor() is interrupted mid-execution.

    • startParse

      public ArchiveServerResponseData startParse(ArchiveServerRequestData request, ArchiveParseType parseType)

      This method starts a new parsing session and returns an archive server response confirming if starting the AO3 parsing was successful.

      Parameters:
      request - The parse request formatted as a ArchiveServerRequestData object.
      parseType - A specific enum from ArchiveParseType.
      Returns:
      An ArchiveServerResponseData object containing whether the parse request was successful.

    • validateSessionId

      public boolean validateSessionId(String sessionId)

      This method validates if a session ID received from a client is formatted properly.

      Parameters:
      sessionId - The session ID received from the client.
      Returns:
      A boolean value for whether the session ID is valid.

    • getSessionInformation

      public ArchiveServerResponseData getSessionInformation(String sessionId)

      This method returns a specific session's information to the archive controller.

      Parameters:
      sessionId - The session ID received from the client.
      Returns:
      An ArchiveServerResponseData object containing the requested session information.

    • getSessionInformationLive

      public ArchiveServerResponseData getSessionInformationLive(String sessionId) throws InterruptedException

      This method starts a live websocket feed for regular session updates and returns a feed start confirmation to the archive controller.

      Parameters:
      sessionId - The session ID received from the client.
      Returns:
      An ArchiveServerResponseData object containing if starting the live feed was successful.
      Throws:
      InterruptedException

    • cancelSession

      public ArchiveServerResponseData cancelSession(String sessionId)

      This method cancels an active session and returns a confirmation to the archive controller.

      Parameters:
      sessionId - The session ID received from the client.
      Returns:
      An ArchiveServerResponseData object containing if canceling the session was successful.
